name: Bershka Tie-Dye Sunset Breeze Graphic T-Shirt
description: A short-sleeve crew neck t-shirt featuring a prominent blue and white spiral tie-dye pattern. The shirt is made from cotton jersey fabric and appears to have a regular or relaxed fit. It includes a small white 'Sunset Breeze' text graphic on the left chest. The back of the shirt displays a large, circular, tribal-style sun graphic, also with 'Sunset Breeze' text integrated into the design, printed in white.

name: Bershka Oversized Striped T-Shirt
description: An oversized short-sleeve t-shirt with a classic crew neck, designed with a relaxed, boxy fit and dropped shoulders for a comfortable silhouette. The shirt features a horizontal stripe pattern across the body and sleeves. The color palette consists of a light pink base, complemented by wider cream stripes and thinner dark teal or grey stripes. The material is a soft cotton jersey, suitable for everyday wear. A very subtle, small embroidered detail is located on the left chest.

name: Erima Classic Logo T-Shirt
description: A classic short-sleeve crew neck t-shirt from the sportswear brand Erima, presented in a solid dusty rose color. This t-shirt is designed with a standard athletic fit, ideal for both training and casual daily wear. The material is a soft and comfortable cotton-blend jersey. The design is minimalist, featuring only a small, contrasting white Erima logo on the left side of the chest. The back of the shirt is plain, maintaining a clean aesthetic.

name: The North Face Mountain Coordinates T-Shirt
description: A classic crew neck t-shirt from The North Face, featured in a solid mustard yellow color. The front is kept simple with a small The North Face logo printed on the left chest. The back makes a statement with a large, rectangular graphic print depicting a mountain landscape, stylized with a vibrant orange sky and a blue-toned mountain. The graphic is overlaid with the text 'Technical Outdoor Equipment' and includes geographic coordinates, emphasizing the brand's spirit of exploration.

name: Erima Classic Logo T-Shirt
description: A classic short-sleeve crew neck t-shirt from the sportswear brand Erima, presented in a solid terracotta red color. This t-shirt is designed with a standard athletic fit, ideal for both training and casual daily wear. The material is a soft and comfortable cotton-blend jersey. The design is minimalist, featuring only a small, contrasting white Erima logo on the left side of the chest. The back of the shirt is plain, maintaining a clean aesthetic.

name: Zara Technical Paneled T-Shirt
description: A short-sleeve performance t-shirt from Zara, presented in a sophisticated two-tone brown. This t-shirt is crafted from a smooth, technical stretch fabric, suggesting properties like moisture-wicking and flexibility. It features a modern, minimalist design with unique paneled construction on the shoulders. The back has a large, geometric color-block panel in a darker shade of brown. A small, black rubberized tag is placed on the front near the hem for a subtle branding detail. The fit is regular, designed for athletic or casual wear.

name: Zara Athleticz Japanese Text T-Shirt
description: A minimalist t-shirt from the Zara Athleticz collection, featured in a solid cream color. This piece is crafted from a high-quality, soft technical fabric with a regular fit, designed for comfort and performance. The front is adorned with a small, black graphic on the left chest, which includes the Japanese Katakana text for 'Balance' (バランス), the number '300', and the Athleticz logo. A signature black rubberized tag is also present on the hem. The back of the t-shirt is kept plain, emphasizing its clean and modern aesthetic.

name: Zara Athleticz Japanese Text T-Shirt
description: This Zara Athleticz Japanese Text T-Shirt features a bold graphic print with Japanese characters on the front of a basic heavy cotton tee.  Available in classic blue and a refreshing light blue, this tee offers a relaxed fit with a crew neckline.

name: Zara Textured Crinkle T-Shirt
description: A minimalist, oversized t-shirt from Zara, presented in a solid dark chocolate brown. The key feature of this piece is its unique, crinkled fabric texture, which provides depth and a tactile quality to the otherwise simple design. It has a relaxed, boxy fit with dropped shoulders for a comfortable and modern silhouette. With no external graphics or logos, this t-shirt is a versatile staple that can be dressed up or down, relying on its distinctive texture to make a statement.

name: Zara Basic Cotton T-Shirt
description: A classic short-sleeve t-shirt from Zara in a solid, muted mauve color. This t-shirt is made from a soft and lightweight cotton jersey, ensuring comfort for everyday wear. It features a regular, classic fit that is versatile and timeless. The design is completely minimalist with no external branding or graphics, making it an essential building block for any wardrobe. It is finished with a standard crew neck and clean hems.

name: Zara Classic Striped T-Shirt
description: A timeless short-sleeve t-shirt from Zara featuring a classic Breton stripe pattern. Made from soft and breathable cotton jersey, this t-shirt offers a comfortable regular fit suitable for everyday wear. The pattern consists of dark navy blue horizontal stripes on a clean white background. It is designed with a solid white ribbed crew neck that provides a neat contrast to the striped body, enhancing its nautical-inspired aesthetic. This piece is a versatile wardrobe staple with no external graphics.

name: adidas Originals Knit Logo T-Shirt
description: A short-sleeve knit top from the adidas Originals collection, presented in a vibrant red with a retro-inspired design. This piece is crafted from a breathable, open-knit cotton fabric that has a crochet-like texture. It features a large, tonal adidas Trefoil logo and wordmark knitted directly into the front using a jacquard technique for a subtle, textured effect. The design is finished with contrasting cream-colored tipping on the ribbed crew neck and sleeve cuffs, enhancing its vintage aesthetic.

name: Puma PUMATECH Pocket T-Shirt
description: A high-performance training t-shirt from Puma's PUMATECH collection, presented in a solid black color. This tee is engineered with a technical, moisture-wicking fabric designed for intense workouts. It features an athletic fit with raglan sleeves for an enhanced range of motion. A standout feature is the large, curved overlay panel on the chest that cleverly integrates a secure vertical zippered pocket for essentials. A reflective Puma cat logo is placed on the chest, and 'PUMATECH' branding adorns the sleeve.

name: Nike Sportswear 'Goddess of Victory' Crop T-Shirt
description: A women's short-sleeve crop top from the Nike Sportswear collection in a solid white color. Crafted from soft cotton jersey, this t-shirt features a fashionable cropped length and a comfortable regular fit. The front has a small, stylized Nike logo in a red script font at the center. The back makes a bold statement with a large graphic print reading 'Goddess of Victory', with 'Goddess' written in the same ornate script and a classic swoosh underneath, all in red. The design is a direct homage to the brand's namesake, the Greek goddess of victory.

name: PSC 'Down To Earth' Washed Rhinestone T-Shirt
description: A short-sleeve graphic t-shirt from PSC with a distinct vintage and streetwear aesthetic. The garment features a bright pink acid wash or mineral wash finish, giving it a uniquely faded and textured look. Made from soft cotton jersey, it offers a comfortable regular fit. The front is decorated with the phrase 'Down To Earth' in a vibrant, neon yellow print, and features a circular graphic below it embellished with sparkling rhinestones. The back remains plain to highlight the washed pattern.

name: Vakkorama 'Pop and Cheers' Graphic T-Shirt
description: A relaxed fit, short-sleeve t-shirt from Vakkorama in a solid periwinkle blue color. Crafted from soft, high-quality cotton jersey, this tee features a comfortable, modern fit. The front is adorned with a small, embroidered graphic of two beverage cans on the left chest. The back makes a bold statement with a large, vibrant pop-art style illustration of the same cans against a swirling purple and white striped background. Below the main artwork, the phrase 'pop one open and cheers' is printed in a playful font.

name: Pegador 'Friends & Family' T-Shirt
description: An oversized t-shirt from the streetwear brand Pegador, featured in a solid off-white color. This t-shirt is crafted from heavyweight cotton, giving it a premium feel and a structured, boxy silhouette. The front is designed with a chest pocket that has a circular black embroidered patch with Pegador branding. The back makes a strong statement with a large, intricate graphic print in black, featuring the text 'FRIENDS & FAMILY' and 'A COMMUNITY BASED ON LOYALTY & UNITY' within a crest-like design.

name: !SOLID Coffee Embroidered T-Shirt
description: A classic short-sleeve crew neck t-shirt from the brand !SOLID, presented in a vibrant solid orange hue. This t-shirt is crafted from soft cotton jersey for all-day comfort and features a standard regular fit. The design is kept minimalist, with the main detail being a small, finely stitched embroidery on the left chest depicting a moka pot and a cup of coffee. The back of the shirt is plain, making it a versatile and understated piece with a charming detail.

name: BASIC PLEASURE MODE Piercing Ring T-Shirt
description: A fitted, 'baby tee' style short-sleeve t-shirt from BASIC PLEASURE MODE in a solid white color. This top is crafted from a stretchy cotton-blend jersey designed for a close-to-the-body fit. The defining feature is its edgy design, with two silver-colored metal captive bead rings pierced through the fabric on the chest, simulating body jewelry. The t-shirt has a classic crew neck and a small metallic brand plaque on the upper back, completing its provocative and alternative look.

name: Dickies 'Workwear Company' Ringer T-Shirt
description: A classic short-sleeve ringer t-shirt from Dickies with a distinct retro feel. The body of the shirt is an off-white or cream color, crafted from comfortable cotton jersey. It features contrasting black ribbed bands on the crew neck and sleeve cuffs, defining its ringer style. The front is printed with the iconic Dickies script logo in black, with 'WORKWEAR COMPANY' text underneath. The back of the tee is plain, maintaining a clean and timeless look.
